where all the parameters are complex, the second term violates the $Z_2$ symmetry, and the terms proportional to $s_i^4/\Lambda _F^4$ are neglected in the first term. Here, $ ar {M}^
u _{23}$ is suppressed with $s_i^2/\Lambda _F^2$, and, as mentioned just below Eq. (11), the scales of $s_i/\Lambda _F$ can be estimated from the charged lepton mass ratio as $s_i/\Lambda _F \sim \sqrt {m_\mu /m_	au }$. Therefore, one can infer $| ar {M}^
